# Build stage
FROM maven:3.9-eclipse-temurin-21 AS builder
WORKDIR /build
COPY pom.xml .
RUN mvn dependency:resolve
COPY src ./src
RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests

# Runtime stage
FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine
RUN apk add --no-cache fontconfig ttf-dejavu curl

# Create non-root user
RUN addgroup -g 1001 app && adduser -D -u 1001 -G app app

# Import AWS RDS root CA and Azure DigiCert certificates
RUN apk add --no-cache openssl && \
    mkdir -p /tmp/certs && \
    wget -O /tmp/certs/rds-ca-2019-root.pem https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/rds-ca-2019-root.pem && \
    wget -O /tmp/certs/rds-ca-rsa2048-g1.pem https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/rds-ca-rsa2048-g1.pem && \
    wget -O /tmp/certs/rds-ca-rsa4096-g1.pem https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/rds-ca-rsa4096-g1.pem && \
    wget -O /tmp/certs/DigiCertGlobalRootG2.crt https://cacerts.digicert.com/DigiCertGlobalRootG2.crt && \
    keytool -import -alias rds-ca-2019 -file /tmp/certs/rds-ca-2019-root.pem -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt || true && \
    keytool -import -alias rds-ca-rsa2048-g1 -file /tmp/certs/rds-ca-rsa2048-g1.pem -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt || true && \
    keytool -import -alias rds-ca-rsa4096-g1 -file /tmp/certs/rds-ca-rsa4096-g1.pem -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt || true && \
    keytool -import -alias digicert-global-root-g2 -file /tmp/certs/DigiCertGlobalRootG2.crt -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt || true && \
    rm -rf /tmp/certs && \
    apk del openssl

WORKDIR /app
COPY --from=builder /build/target/*.jar /app/app.jar
RUN chown -R app:app /app

USER app

EXPOSE 3000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=40s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

ENTRYPOINT ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
